### **4. 23_RealTimeLineChart**  
**Description:**  
Plots streaming numeric data in real time using Matplotlib.

#### **README.md**
```markdown
# RealTimeLineChart - Live Data Plot Visualizer

RealTimeLineChart is a minimal real-time charting tool for monitoring metrics, simulations, or sensor data.

## Features
- Smooth line rendering  
- Scrollable time axis  
- Works with any numeric source  

## Usage
```bash
git clone https://github.com/your-username/23_RealTimeLineChart.git
cd 23_RealTimeLineChart
python visualize.py
